{{Top|leg}}
An '''identification beacon''' was a device built into the [[Concussion missile/Legends|concussion missiles]] of the [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE Bomber]] that helped the weapon lock onto the correct target.

It could, however, be disrupted by some planetary [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmospheres]] which would confuse the beacon and cause it to stray from its intended path. An example of this occurred on [[Qlothos]] when a missile inadvertently hit a residential community a kilometer away from what was thought to be a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] garrison.

